Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are. I'll never see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry up and catch Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world-class top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter that people\Nlike you can get involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for the igniters\Nto go off. We have to hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a rare occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you something\Ninteresting before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cat-Cat Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leopard Model...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A leopard human...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that appearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:39.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:57.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:04.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:11.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:19.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:22.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:37.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:48.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:52.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:04.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:23.07,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Straw Hat Pirates Annihilated?\NThe Menace of the Leopard Model!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...! Is this the pirates' doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must still be a lot of people left inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Iceberg-san?!\NWhat's going on upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The rest of you, put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the fire has started to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you're a\Nleopard human or what, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't let you lay a finger on Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Carnivore Zoan types\Nbecome more brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Logia types,\NZoan types, and Paramythia types...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many unique powers exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genuine physical augmentation\Nis the trait of Zoan types.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more we train, the stronger we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zoan type is the strongest species\Nwhen it comes to a close attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear stuff\Nabout monsters like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to waste time, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we have to take care of you guys\Nbefore we get wrapped up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foremen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci... the craftsmen are coming upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. They can't make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! The ceiling is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you out of this place no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible! Your injuries\Nare too severe! How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call my name... as if we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get... out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I considered you guys my friends all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pigeon jerk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice flight off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma! There's a big fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Galley-La's main office.\NWhat a terrible thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible thing? Did someone set the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but often, a bad feeling turns out to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Iceberg is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this is all because of\Nthat thing. It just shouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What pirates say cannot be evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident will now be shrouded in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san... No matter how good\Nof a shipbuilding engineer you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're the mayor of a big city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, a mere citizen, shouldn't have disobeyed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the powerful World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. We'll find Tom's\Nother disciple Franky--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather, Cutty Flam, and take\Nthe blueprints from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get everyone out of the building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go inside anymore!\NHave each team account for its men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Iceberg-san? Did you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's still in this fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of our foremen are with him.\NThere's no way he got left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go check around there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the Straw Hats. There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she jump out a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was probably surrounded by\Nflames and had trouble escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... what a terrible thing they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make her tell us where the others are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll capture all of them and\Nhand them over to the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno... So Franky was at your bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he rushed out to find Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he doesn't stay in one place for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people with bad timing really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got Long-nose with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want him to sing in the key of C...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's not it! How many\Ntimes do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "If you don't want him to sink in the sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the key of C...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the sea"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what were you listening to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is to get the\Nmessage to Straw Hat, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saying that message ain't gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro is gonna beat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say it like, "If you don't\Nwant him to sink in the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come to the warehouse under the bridge!\NFranky sends his regards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you, even if he comes, Bro is\Ngonna beat the crap out of him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you say is waiting for whom where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're busy right now! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna die,\Nanswer my question in three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what family we're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which place do you mean by\Nthe warehouse under the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky is there, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have with Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna talk to him, then talk to us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you left the friends\Nyou traveled together with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way from the East Blue, for the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! We're not crying, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I was moved by your\Nprotecting this ship all by yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while all those things were happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not crying! None of us are crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is their problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, now you know that those guys\Nand I are no longer friends, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about your hardships!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The song title is, "Severed Friendship!\NNorthern Wind Chop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the tea ready yet? I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll bring it right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted from crying...\NNot that I cried, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Bro. It's a little hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I get it, brother, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down a little, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a break\Nand have some tea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame you. You must be\Nholding quite a grudge against us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for taking 200 million Berries\Naway from you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since it led to such a big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was meant to happen, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding a grudge doesn't do me any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That 200 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it all, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to knock you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've shown me how manly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now I have to calm my anger\Nover the complete destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Franky House, which was\Nmy home and demolition factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you guys\Nannihilated my subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro!\N--The anger welled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, brother, although a lot happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's calm our anger towards\Neach other on this matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and settle it as "Heave-ho! Heave-ho!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "fifty-fifty."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "fifty-fifty," Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do now that you're alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nowhere to go anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I can\Ntake you in. Work for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I don't wanna\Nbecome a demolition worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I left my group, I'm still a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to my song.\NIt's titled "The Pirate Code."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I'm trying to think what\Nyou should do next, for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, is it okay for you\Nto relax in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm surge is coming soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Aqua Laguna comes,\Nwe all have to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now until late into the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,houses will be submerged\Nup to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in the backstreets or capes at\Na time like this, you don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry if\Nyou keep your ship here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Thanks... I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! Don't act like we're strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it must be tough to have\Nflood damage like that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone's used to this\Nannual evacuation, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more problematic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that the water level of the sea\Nhas been increasing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The backstreet area you can see above\Nthe sea now is a town built on the rooftops
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of an old town that existed\Nseveral hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that the shipbuilding\Nisland and the backstreets
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were completely on one land a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, so much of the area is under\Nwater that it's called a floating city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the sidewalks became canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Properly speaking, rather than saying\Nthat the water level is increasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they say that the foundation\Nof the island is sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, the areas in town we can\Nlive in will get smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Even this pretty floating\Ncity has hardships too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, if push comes to shove,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can take the sea train\Nand go live somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was only a bit over a decade\Nago that the sea train was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that time, it wasn't quite\Nthat easy to go across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, people were rarely able to\Ngo back and forth between the islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this isolated island,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the residents vaguely imagined\Ntheir land being submerged someday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and grew completely hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What relieved people's\Nworries even about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the sea train, Puffing Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can now go across the sea\Nwhenever you want without a Log Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was big progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea train really is an incredible thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Seven came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to a great shipwright\Nnamed Tom who created the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say hello to "Bro" for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now know the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:33.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:38.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:47.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:56.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:07.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:15.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Long-nose. What're you\Ngonna do after you fix that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else? I'll go on an\Nadventure with her again and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--That ship can't even reach\Nthe next island anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you demolish that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Man Who Is Loved Even\Nby His Ship! Usopp's Tears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
